AssertionError: 复制平仓总手数不匹配，预期: 1.00, 实际: 2.0
assert False
 +  where False = <built-in function isclose>(1.0, 2.0, rel_tol=1e-09, abs_tol=1e-09)
 +    where <built-in function isclose> = math.isclose
 +    and   1.0 = float('1.00')
 +    and   2.0 = float(2.0)

 +    where <built-in function isclose> = math.isclose
 +    and   1.0 = float('1.00')
 +    and   0.8 = float(0.8)
